data.meta_desc: DRAGON'S BLOOD 8/10 AS someone who have never played the game.. .. but who loves fantasy elves dragons magic and 2D animated action sequences of the highest possible caliber, I applaud this show. I knew absolutely nothing about this world or characters going in, but binged the entire season and can't wait for more. Of course it's a glorified commercial for the game, but when commercials are this good I couldn't care less. To produce this kind of anime with this amount of hand drawn animations isn't cheap though. So I really hope Valve/Netflix or who ever is paying the bill keeps doing it for many more seasons. Cause this is really good television. And to whoever designed the dragons: hat off to you. Memes.
